sequenceDiagram
    participant E as Editor
    participant UI as Dashboard UI
    participant API as Editor API
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant AL as Audit Logger

    E->>UI: Access Dashboard
    UI->>API: GET /editor/dashboard/stats
    API->>DB: Query submissions
    DB-->>API: Return data
    API-->>UI: Statistics
    UI-->>E: Display stats

    E->>UI: View Submission
    UI->>API: GET /editor/submissions/:id
    API->>DB: Fetch submission + tasks
    DB-->>API: Submission data
    API-->>UI: Full details
    UI-->>E: Show details

    E->>UI: Make Decision
    UI->>API: POST /editor/submissions/:id/decision
    API->>DB: Save decision
    API->>AL: Log action
    DB-->>API: Success
    AL-->>API: Logged
    API-->>UI: Confirmation
    UI-->>E: Decision recorded
